3,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T03:41:34.000Z","msg":"如果仲係黑鬼總統同支那貿易談判會有幾廢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T03:53:47.000Z","msg":"如果希拉里當選總統呢？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T04:10:28.000Z","msg":"跟本連談判都冇<br />\n民主黨只會繼續自欺欺人，養肥支那<br />\n然後集中搞極左政策，如green deal，女權/黑人/蛔優先，煽動反白人/男人/基督教情緒"},{"pid":"4b2f1fcbfbd52e765f65ccad0a27c2e1251dc6c1","tid":1142180,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T04:12:41.000Z","msg":".S. Trade Representative Robert Lighthizer, who has been an advocate for tough structural changes in China, said Beijing had reneged on commitments it had made previously that would have changed the agreement substantially.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Over the course of the last week or so we have seen ... an erosion in commitments by China,&rdquo; Lighthizer told reporters. &ldquo;That in our view is unacceptable.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n⋯<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;We&rsquo;re not breaking off talks at this point. But for now ... come Friday there will be tariffs in place,&rdquo; Lighthizer said.<br />\n<br />\nTreasury Secretary Steven Mnuchin, considered to be less hawkish toward China, said China&rsquo;s backtracking became clear with &ldquo;new information&rdquo; over the weekend. He declined to give specifics and said the U.S. side had originally hoped to conclude a deal one way or the other this week.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;They were trying to go back on language that had been previously negotiated, very clear language, that had the potential of changing the deal dramatically,&rdquo; Mnuchin said. &ldquo;The entire economic team ... are completely unified and recommended to the president to move forward with tariffs if we are not able to conclude a deal by the end of the week.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-trade-china/u-s-china-reneged-on-trade-commitments-sparking-trump-tariff-hike-idUSKCN1SC0MF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-usa-trade-china%2Fu-s-china-reneged-on-trade-commitments-sparking-trump-tariff-hike-idUSKCN1SC0MF&d=BbGirfR5U81eMP64OYU5HAZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=e328df61\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-usa-trade-china%2Fu-s-china-reneged-on-trade-commitments-sparking-trump-tariff-hike-idUSKCN1SC0MF&h=acaeaef2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-trade-china/u-s-china-reneged-on-trade-commitments-sparking-trump-tariff-hike-idUSKCN1SC0MF</a>"},{"pid":"eedc79eec825f1383f5938718d7ed60b316d81a8","tid":1142180,"uid":49812,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d809ef4a2687483c16fb0e5a70fd7eb42cf4588c","tid":1142180,"uid":215225,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"5931dc7b14722b5ff0c17d59a5a4ee32c9026f3d","tid":1142180,"uid":49812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f433eeed76d82fa33af120f706f78885020f9c72","tid":1142180,"uid":156363,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T03:41:34.000Z","msg":"如果仲係黑鬼總統同支那貿易談判會有幾廢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T03:53:47.000Z","msg":"如果希拉里當選總統呢？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T04:10:28.000Z","msg":"跟本連談判都冇<br />\n民主黨只會繼續自欺欺人，養肥支那<br />\n然後集中搞極左政策，如green deal，女權/黑人/蛔優先，煽動反白人/男人/基督教情緒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T04:14:51.000Z","msg":"仲會養肥愛中共國既ABC、移民、留學生添"},{"pid":"3869fbd25d992fd392d1593eb5f1590ddf307cf5","tid":1142180,"uid":37232,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T04:18:32.000Z","msg":"叫中國履行晒入WTO的承諾先可以傾貿易協議"},{"pid":"cec9ccf0ad3a5e82724a9bce55963a45d5c4e676","tid":1142180,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1720672d720be27805761ae4beac7315089ae3fe","tid":1142180,"uid":245441,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T03:54:24.000Z","msg":"BFW 05/07 03:40 *環球時報社評：即使美國全面加徵關稅，也不意味著談判的大門關閉<br />\nBFW 05/07 03:38 *DOOR ISN'T CLOSED TO TRADE TALKS IF U.S. RAISES TARIFFS: GT<br />\nBFW 05/07 03:38 *環球時報社評：談判破裂對中國產生的綜合衝擊將是可